OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FClimate change pioneer     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FClaude Lorius dies at 91   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Claude Lorius, a leading glaciologist  
OL,6, whose expeditions helped prove that    
OL,7, humans were responsible for global     
OL,8, warming, has died at the age of 91.    
OL,10,FHe led 22 expeditions to Greenland and 
OL,11,FAntarctica during his lifetime.        
OL,13,FIt was during one trip to Antarctica in
OL,14,F1965 where an evening of whiskey with  
OL,15,Fice cubes led him to prove humankind's 
OL,16,Frole in the heating of the Earth's     
OL,17,Fsurface.                               
OL,19,FLorius died on Tuesday morning in the  
OL,20,FFrench region of Burgundy.             
